    koza "¡¿Mmm?!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:245
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_409eb501:

    # koza "[vivi.n]... It's been so long..."
    koza "[vivi.n]... Ha pasado tanto tiempo..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:246
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_fe323106:

    # koza "I thought your disappearance was part of the king's plot."
    koza "Pensé que tu desaparición era parte del complot del rey."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:247
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_13021026:

    # koza "I didn't think you'd be around here..."
    koza "No pensé que estarías por aquí..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:248
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_6a2d6981:

    # koza "I'm glad you made it this far..."
    koza "Me alegro de que hayas llegado hasta aquí..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:249
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_2ba2b7de:

    # koza "If you're here, I suppose you know everything..."
    koza "Si estás aquí supongo que ya lo sabes todo..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:250
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_a33c4e3d:

    # koza "I won't blame you for what your father did... But... You can't stop me!"
    koza "No te culparé por lo que hizo tu padre... Pero... ¡No puedes detenerme!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:251
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_416fe5c4:

    # koza "Your father has crossed the line today... There's no way to stop the people's anger."
    koza "Tu padre hoy ha cruzado la línea... No hay forma de detener la ira del pueblo."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:253
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_7ece6f50:

    # vivi "[koza.n], I understand your anger, but it's not what it seems. Let me explain everything quickly."
    vivi "[koza.n] Entiendo tu enojo, pero no es lo que parece. Déjame explicarte todo rápidamente."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:254
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_f07d7f5e:

    # vivi "This man here, has the power of a strange devil fruit, he dressed up and changed his face like the king.... He is an impostor, the real culprit behind this chaos."
    vivi "Este hombre aquí, tiene el poder de una extraña fruta del diablo, se vistió y cambió su rostro como el rey... Él es un impostor, el verdadero culpable detrás de este caos."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:255
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_bac63762:

    # vivi "My group and this boy are witnesses."
    vivi "Mi grupo y este chico son testigos."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:256
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_2ed9f4da:

    # vivi "We managed to defeat him and bring him here as proof!"
    vivi "¡Logramos derrotarlo y traerlo aquí como prueba!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:257
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_53767b1a:

    # vivi "But he's just a subordinate. The true mastermind is [crocodile.n]!"
    vivi "Pero él es solo un subordinado. ¡El verdadero cerebro es [crocodile.n]!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:259
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_98a07135:

    # koza "Mnmn... The owner of the Rains Diner and casino?"
    koza "Mmm... ¿El dueño del Rains Diner y Casino?"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:260
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_5c0b8f9a:

    # koza "Mnmnm... It's pretty hard to believe all this."
    koza "Mmmm... Es bastante difícil creer todo esto."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:262
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_f2154373:

    # vivi "I know, it's completely insane... But let me explain everything briefly."
    vivi "Lo sé, es una locura total... Pero os lo voy a explicar todo brevemente."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:263
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_1b04e036:

    # vivi "You owe me that much after so many years of friendship!"
    vivi "¡Me debes mucho después de tantos años de amistad!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:265
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_cd4f9287:

    # koza "... Fine, you have a point. Tell me everything you know!"
    koza "Bien, tienes razón. ¡Cuéntame todo lo que sepas!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:266
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_59b279b0:

    # vivi "Perfect! It all started when we decided to infiltrate [crocodile.n]'s organization along with [igaram.n]..."
    vivi "¡Perfecto! Todo empezó cuando decidimos infiltrarnos en la organización de [crocodile.n] junto con [igaram.n]..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:273
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_9d42f3b0:

    # narrador "You take your time to explain everything to [koza.n]."
    narrador "Te tomas tu tiempo para explicarle todo a [koza.n]."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:275
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_166d9a85:

    # koza "I can't believe all of this is happening..."
    koza "No puedo creer que todo esto esté pasando..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:276
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_bc3ec0ee:

    # koza "That bastard [mr2.n] tricked us all..."
    koza "Ese bastardo [mr2.n] nos engañó a todos..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:277
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_0b553e8d:

    # koza "I must stop the fighting..."
    koza "Debo detener la pelea..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:279
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_b11de529:

    # vivi "Yes, you have to stop this! I'm sure you can do it!"
    vivi "¡Sí, tienes que parar esto! ¡Seguro que puedes!"

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Nanohana/ar_nanohana_h.rpy:280
translate spanish ar_nanohana_h_9b11f34b:

    # vivi "With this evidence, you can calm things down a little..."
    vivi "Con esta evidencia se puede calmar un poco la situación..."

